high_descs: Turn left, go to the fridge, turn left, go to the counter with the bottle on it.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn right, go a few feet, turn left, bring the spoon across the room to the sink.
Put the spoon in the mug on the counter, right of the sink.
Pick up the mug with spoon on the counter.
Put the mug with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter on the left.
Pick up the spoon to the right of the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn right, hang a left at the fridge and walk to the sink.
Put the spoon inside the white mug to the right of the sink on the counter.
Pick up the mug with the spoon inside from the counter.
Put the mug with the spoon inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a spoon in a sink.

high_descs: Turn left, go towards the fridge, turn left and approach the counter.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Turn right, go halfway across the room, turn left and go to the sink.
Put the spoon in the white cup.
Pick up the white cup with the spoon in it.
Put the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a cup in the sink.
